sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client (service)
    participant GW as hmac_auth middleware
    participant H as hmac_verifier.py
    participant V as Vault
    participant R as Redis (nonce store)
    participant EP as Endpoint /api/service

    Note over C: Tự ký: dựng canonical request<br/>-> string-to-sign -> HMAC-SHA256
    C->>GW: POST /api/service + X-Key-Id, X-Timestamp,<br/>X-Nonce, X-Signature + body
    GW->>H: verify_hmac_request(...)
    H->>H: 1-2. Parse 4 header + check format
    H->>H: 3. |now - timestamp| <= 300s? (chống timestamp cũ)
    H->>R: 4. nonce đã tồn tại? (chống replay)
    R-->>H: có -> replay_detected (401)
    H->>V: 5. Lấy secret theo X-Key-Id
    V-->>H: secret (hoặc dev fallback)
    H->>H: 6-8. Dựng lại chữ ký kỳ vọng từ secret + body
    H->>H: 9. compare_digest(expected, signature) constant-time
    H->>R: 10. SETEX nonce TTL 600s (đánh dấu đã dùng)
    H-->>GW: OK hoặc raise HMACInvalid
    GW->>EP: cho qua
    EP-->>C: 200 verified
